batch_size = 10
cell_params = torch.randn(batch_size, 6) * 10 + 100  # Random variations

crystals = []
for i in range(batch_size):
    config = CrystalConfig(
        cell_a=cell_params[i, 0],
        cell_b=cell_params[i, 1],
        # ... etc
    )
    crystals.append(Crystal(config=config))
```

